    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Reurlet 6/8/54.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "You are instructed to recontact [REDACTED], referred to",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "in your referenced letter and advise him this Bureau has no",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "jurisdiction concerning the investigation of matters relating",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "to flying discs and that the United States Air Force has such",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "jurisdiction. You are instructed to advise him this Bureau cannot",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "approve or disapprove of his activities in connection with this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "matter and that the placing of this Bureau on notice as to his",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "activities will not exonerate him in the event he engages in any",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "fraudulent or criminal activities.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "You are instructed to furnish the information set forth",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "in your referenced letter to OSI locally and to the Bureau in a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "memorandum suitable for dissemination to OSI headquarters.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "NOTE: [REDACTED] Cincinnati, Ohio, advised the Cincinnati",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "office he is interested in flying discs and has recently met several",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "persons who claimed to have had experiences with flying discs. He",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "stated he intended to assist such persons in arranging for public",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "meeting in Cincinnati, at which matters relating to flying discs",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "will be discussed and that he expects the meeting will result",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "in a \"four thousand dollar take.\" He advised he believed the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "experiences alleged by the persons referred to above and that those",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "persons would participate in the meeting. He stated he had been",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "advised by the Air Force that it was it's opinion claims made by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "the persons referred to above concerning flying discs and their",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "experiences with same were fraudulent. He stated he wanted to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "put all federal agencies on notice in order that they could act to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
